      "writtenOn": "2018-04-13T12:18:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Depot tools has this very unfortunate self-update feature which runs before executing certain commands.  See https://chromium.googlesource.com/chromium/tools/depot_tools/+/master/update_depot_tools#115 We pin depot tools to a specific version and therefore don\u0027t want it updating itself without our consent.",
